gov.cms.qrda.schematron.merge

Class SchematronMerge

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.cms.qrda.schematron.merge.SchematronMerge

  • public class SchematronMerge
extends java.lang.Object
    The class implements the process of merging schematron template files into a single schematron file. It creates XML Document objects for each of the schematron files to merge, and parses each document, gathering the appropriate sections withing each, and writing them out in a particular order into a single merged document file.
    Author:
    Shon Vick, ESAC Inc., additions by Dan Donahue ESAC Inc.
